DEUTSCHE BANK NATIONAL TRUST COMPANY AMERICAS, AS TRUSTEE FOR MORTGAGE ASSET-BACKED PASS-THROUGH CERTIFICATES, SERIES 2006-Q09, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Janet SPINELLI f/k/a Janet Campisi, State of New Jersey, and United States of America, Defendants,
and
Louis Spinelli, Defendant-Petitioner. C-702 September Term 2018
082077 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003642-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
